## Key Publication Areas

My research spans several key areas:

### Paleoclimate Synthesis & Data-Model Integration
- Arctic temperature reconstructions
- Global climate synthesis through PAGES 2k network
- Data assimilation approaches for paleoclimate

### Paleoclimate Informatics
- LiPD (Linked Paleo Data) format development
- Linked Earth platform and ontology development
- Paleoclimate data standardization

### Lake-Based Climate Reconstructions  
- San Juan Mountains paleoclimate records
- Dust-drought interactions in the southwestern US
- High-resolution climate variability

### Process-Based Paleoclimate Modeling
- Glacier-lake system modeling
- Arctic paleoclimate dynamics
- Climate proxy system modeling

